VhDir Digital Certificate Standard Value Set

Codes for documenting VHDir Digital Certificate Standard

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/ig/vhdir/CodeSystem/codesystem-digitalCertificate
    CodeDisplay
    x.509v3x.509v3The digital certificate standard defines the framework of the public key certificates and the atribute certitficates. It also defines a framework for the provision of authentication services.
